Help on skill: slaughter slash
Skill type: offensive
Usage duration: automatic
Affecting stats: Str/Dex

This skill is a part of the martial artists way of combat.
Your skill percent affects how often this skill works.
Slaughter slash is the most devastating offensive melee
attack, but it's much harder to perform than the other ones.
You always hit with the most efficient blow that succeeds.
One needs a sword to use this maneuver.

